# Trivy Ignore File
# These CVEs affect OS packages in python:3.13-slim (Debian) with no upstream fix.
# Reviewed: 2026-05-19. Re-review by: 2026-08-31.

# ncurses buffer overflow — not used by application code (terminal library)
CVE-2025-69720

# systemd arbitrary code execution — not the init system inside containers
CVE-2026-29111

# nghttp2 DoS — base image residual; not used by application code
CVE-2026-27135

# glibc iconv() DoS — fix deferred by Debian; app does not use iconv with untrusted character sets
CVE-2026-4046

# curl / libcurl4t64 — SMB connection reuse and cookie leak; app uses HTTPS only, not SMB
# Reviewed: 2026-05-19. Re-review by: 2026-08-31.
CVE-2026-5773
CVE-2026-6276

# libgnutls30t64 — all DTLS-specific vulnerabilities (zero-length fragment DoS, NUL-char auth bypass,
# heap overflow, nameConstraints bypass, packet reordering DoS, name constraint bypass);
# app makes TCP/HTTPS calls only with no DTLS exposure. No Debian fix available.
# Reviewed: 2026-05-19. Re-review by: 2026-08-31.
CVE-2026-33845
CVE-2026-42010
CVE-2026-33846
CVE-2026-3833
CVE-2026-42009
CVE-2026-42011

# libssh2 integer overflow via large username/password — app does not use SSH in any container
# Reviewed: 2026-05-19. Re-review by: 2026-08-31.
CVE-2026-7598

# libkrb5 / Kerberos DoS via integer underflow (libgssapi-krb5-2, libk5crypto3, libkrb5-3, libkrb5support0)
# No Debian fix available. App does not use Kerberos or GSSAPI; these packages are
# transitive OS-level dependencies of the python:3.13-slim base image.
# Reviewed: 2026-05-21. Re-review by: 2026-08-31.
CVE-2026-40356

# perl-base — Archive::Tar symlink/hardlink path traversal, IO::Compress arbitrary code execution,
# Perl heap buffer overflow, and memory exhaustion via crafted archives.
# No Debian fix available. App is a Python-only data ingestion pipeline (JSON fetch → pandas → GCS).
# perl-base is a transitive OS-level dependency of python:3.13-slim; Perl is never invoked at runtime.
# Reviewed: 2026-06-03. Re-review by: 2026-09-30.
CVE-2026-42496
CVE-2026-8376
CVE-2026-42497
CVE-2026-48962
CVE-2026-9538
